قاعده 1: اگر f(x) = \sqrt{ax+b} و ax+b > 0 باشد، آنگاه f'(x) = \frac{a}{2\sqrt{ax+b}}.
اثبات:
f'(x) = \lim_{h \to 0} \frac{f(x+h) - f(x)}{h} = \lim_{h \to 0} \frac{\sqrt{a(x+h)+b} - \sqrt{ax+b}}{h}
= \lim_{h \to 0} \frac{(\sqrt{a(x+h)+b} - \sqrt{ax+b})(\sqrt{a(x+h)+b} + \sqrt{ax+b})}{h(\sqrt{a(x+h)+b} + \sqrt{ax+b})}
= \lim_{h \to 0} \frac{ax+ah+b-ax-b}{h(\sqrt{a(x+h)+b} + \sqrt{ax+b})} = \lim_{h \to 0} \frac{a}{\sqrt{a(x+h)+b} + \sqrt{ax+b}} = \frac{a}{2\sqrt{ax+b}}

قاعده 2: اگر f(x) = \sqrt[3]{x} آنگاه f'(x) = \frac{1}{3\sqrt[3]{x^2}}.
اثبات:
f'(x) = \lim_{h \to 0} \frac{f(x+h) - f(x)}{h} = \lim_{h \to 0} \frac{\sqrt[3]{x+h} - \sqrt[3]{x}}{h}
= \lim_{h \to 0} \frac{(\sqrt[3]{x+h} - \sqrt[3]{x})(\sqrt[3]{(x+h)^2} + \sqrt[3]{x(x+h)} + \sqrt[3]{x^2})}{h(\sqrt[3]{(x+h)^2} + \sqrt[3]{x(x+h)} + \sqrt[3]{x^2})}
= \lim_{h \to 0} \frac{x+h-x}{h(\sqrt[3]{(x+h)^2} + \sqrt[3]{x(x+h)} + \sqrt[3]{x^2})} = \frac{1}{3\sqrt[3]{x^2}}
